  <brief_title>Magnetic Stimulation as a Treatment for Auditory Hallucinations in Schizophrenia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Transcranial Magnetic Stimulation Used to Treat Auditory Hallucinations in Schizophrenia</official_title>
